EasyAsPy -- Based on Scratch by MIT
======
EasyAsPy is a Python framework that allows the use of Scratch-like commands.
It will eventually have a 'stage' area like Scratch by using Pygame.
======
To get started now:
Install Python (3.x and up not yet supported)
Download the latest version of EasyAsPy
Place files in your user directory
-Debian-based Linux-
Get to the terminal window
Type in 'cd ~/EasyAsPy'
Type in 'python'
Type in 'from easyaspy import *'
You're done!
